While there is dispute concerning the crisis in Iraq, we must not allow ourselves to be divided on fundamental issues here in this European Parliament; 

    on the contrary

, where those fundamental issues are concerned, the road into the future is one on which we must journey together.

Let us in future do everything possible to prevent axes from being again established between capitals, with one city ranged against the other; 
          instead
        , we Europeans must act as a Community.
